14 failure to vote as prescribed in Section 4-120.2 of this title;
15 7. The surrendering of the voter’s Oklahoma driver license to
16 Service Oklahoma upon being issued a driver license in another
17 state; or
18 8. Being excused from jury duty for not being a citizen of the
19 United States; or
20 9. Determination that the voter is not a citizen of the United
21 States.
